Novolipetsk Seeks Alcoa’s Wieser, Ex-Voestalpine CEO for Board

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-05-16T13:38:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/novolipetsk-seeks-alcoa-s-wieser-ex-voestalpine-ceo-for-board.html
OAO Novolipetsk Steel,  Russia ’s
largest steelmaker by market value, nominated an executive from
Alcoa Inc. and a former chief executive officer of Voestalpine
AG for election by shareholders as independent directors.  The Lipetsk, Russia-based company proposed Helmut Wieser,
Alcoa’s executive vice president, and former Voestalpine CEO
Franz Struzl as candidates, documents for a June 3 shareholder
meeting provided by the steelmaker’s press office show.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
 ajordan11@bloomberg.net  